---
title: Peri Peri Chicken Burger and Chips with Charred Sweetcorn Salad and Zesty Garlic Mayo
description: This Peri Peri Chicken Burger and Chips is a luxurious dinner night option, made with premium ingredients for a real taste of luxury at home!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R31_W11_UK_SSF4463-12_Main_high-e306e520.jpg
